# Silverstripe Assets Gallery Module
Turns assets folder into basic gallery with slideshow.

## Maintainer contact
 * Marijn Kampf (Nickname: marijnkampf)
  <marijn at exadium dot com>
   
   http://www.exadium.com/tools/silverstripe/modules/
   
   Sponsored by Exadium Web Development

## Requirements
SilverStripe 3.1

##Documentation
###Installation
* Download from github
* Create page with Assets Gallery page type
* Enter subfolder in settings e.g. /gallery/

Works with Breadcrumbnavigation module https://github.com/marijnkampf/Silverstripe-Module-BreadcrumbNavigation

Image gallery lightbox / colorbox based on code by unclecheese: http://www.silverstripe.org/imagegallery-module/
